title: So i played my 10 provisionals, now i have no rank?
body: i finally played all my provisionals on my smurf "Dip Sucks" even tho doing very well every game i lost 6 and won 4... anyway i didnt get anything after my last one, now it says i have no rank can someone help please :/

replies.body:
It means you missed out on bronze division.
Try again when season resets.
Thats what happened to me but I played one more game and I got my rank
